abstract: Nasdaq OMX Group reports third-quarter profit of $110 million, or 61 cents per share, up 8.9 percent from year-ago quarter; revenue was $438 million, up 18 percent.
snippet: Trading volume on United States exchanges surged 14 percent from a year earlier as investors speculated that the European debt crisis was spreading.
lead_paragraph: Trading volume on United States exchanges surged 14 percent from a year earlier as investors speculated that the European debt crisis was spreading.
